36:35.670 --> 36:37.000
Reporter #2: Ms. Keating,
there's speculation

36:37.000 --> 36:38.960
you wouldn't have gotten
this not guilty verdict

36:38.960 --> 36:40.290
if you hadn't made the trial

36:40.290 --> 36:42.000
all about the Governor
and the FBI.

36:42.000 --> 36:43.880
I would never presume
to know why

36:43.880 --> 36:45.580
the jury decided
to side with me.

36:45.580 --> 36:47.670
Either way,
it's clear that they saw through

36:47.670 --> 36:50.920
Governor Birkhead's weak attempt
to make me the guilty party here

36:50.920 --> 36:53.210
when it's actually her.

36:53.210 --> 36:54.790
Were you aware
the Governor's here today?

36:54.790 --> 36:58.080
Probably here to
watch me win.

36:58.080 --> 37:00.380
Uh, no. She's meeting
