Eve: Thank you.

38:34.620 --> 38:37.330
Bonnie: Frank.
Frank, I'm here.

38:37.330 --> 38:39.120
I'm here. I'm here.

38:39.120 --> 38:41.210
I had to make it right.

38:42.120 --> 38:43.500
No.

38:43.500 --> 38:45.380
Tell Annalise.

38:45.380 --> 38:47.250
No, you --
you can tell her.

38:47.250 --> 38:48.830
You're gonna tell her.
Annalise: Bonnie!

38:48.830 --> 38:50.380
No, you tell her.

38:50.380 --> 38:53.420
Bonnie. Bonnie.
You tell her.

38:53.420 --> 38:56.330
What -- Oh, what did --

38:56.330 --> 38:58.670
Why -- Why did he...
Why?!

38:58.670 --> 39:00.380
Why did he...

39:02.880 --> 39:04.380
Okay.

39:04.380 --> 39:05.790
Oh. Oh, no.

39:05.790 --> 39:07.880
Help! Help!

39:07.880 --> 39:08.920
She's been shot!

39:08.920 --> 39:10.880
Help me! Help!

39:10.880 --> 39:12.710
No, Bonnie!

39:12.710 --> 39:14.670
Bonnie! Bonnie, no!

39:14.670 --> 39:17.080
Stay with me!

39:17.080 --> 39:18.620
Stay with me!

39:18.620 --> 39:20.380
Bonnie! No!

39:20.380 --> 39:21.710
Stay!

39:21.710 --> 39:23.670
Bonnie, no!

39:23.670 --> 39:27.540
Eve: What words can make meaning
out of an entire life

39:27.540 --> 39:29.210
