for everything.

40:48.920 --> 40:51.250
I think that's why
so many of us are here today.

40:51.250 --> 40:53.290
To remember her, yes.

40:53.290 --> 40:55.460
But also to forgive her.

40:55.460 --> 41:00.710
♪ As the sun waits to eclipse ♪

41:00.710 --> 41:05.620
